Products.Name: Helga's Sourdough Wraps
Products.SupplyLimitMessage: 'Helga's Sourdough Wraps' has a supply limit of 36. The quantity in your cart has been reduced accordingly. To purchase a larger quantity, please contact us on 1800 000 610. Please note we do not supply trade orders.
Products.RichDescription:
Helga’s Sourdough Wraps are thin, round and flat. They are 10 inches in diameter, a creamy light brown colour with golden brown toast marks and have a subtly sour, satisfying tangy flavour. They are very soft and pliable texture making it a multipurpose wrap.

Helga's bakers begin with care by selecting the best quality ingredients, those that bring out the best taste in each other. Including rye sourdough for flavour to delight your senses with a subtly sour, satisfying tangy flavour.

WHY NOT TRY?
Use wraps to make salad bowls. Simply place the wrap in a greased oven proof bowl and bake until crispy! Fill with salad leaves and your choice of ingredients.

IT'S NOT JUST BREAD. IT'S HELGA'S®
SOURDOUGH
- Lower in Sodium†
- Source of Fibre
- Source of Protein
- Suitable for Vegans
- No Artificial Colours, Flavours or Preservatives
- No Added Sugar
- 3.5 Health Star Rating & Health Star Rating Chart

†30% less sodium than other leading brands compared to 620mg/100g average for 80% of the wraps market (January 2020).
